The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Santosh Trophy 

Srinagar: Jammu and Kashmir will host the Santosh Trophy football championship in June-July this year. Arrangements for hosting the championship at Polo Ground here are in full swing, minister of state for sports and youth services Babu Singh said. 

The event was supposed to be hosted last year but postponed due to security reasons. (PTI) 




